{"tid":956792,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★勵志！夫家千億遺產 李嘉欣月領200萬零用錢","createTime":"2018-12-26T14:29:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-26T15:05:46.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"ade49f8d2cc424f4257166db965cfb615f7ba64f","tid":956792,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T14:29:40.000Z","msg":"港澳著名女模特兒、女演員李嘉欣，10年前嫁給香港船王許愛周之孫許晉亨。日前公公許世勳病逝後，留下420億港幣（約1651億元台幣）資產，引發外界關注，這筆高額資產該如何分配。<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，女星李嘉欣的公公許世勳，日前不幸病逝，據了解，許世勳過去將財產全都投入家族信託基金與巨額保單，所以家人無法直接繼承遺產，但是李嘉欣和老公許晉亨，<span style=\"color: red;\">每個月可以領取200萬港幣（約786萬元台幣）的「零用錢」</span>，由此可見許世勳替子女細心的安排，對他們愛護有加。<br />\n<br />\n許世勳相當看重兒子許晉亨，對孫子Jayden更是疼愛，曾經砸下500萬港幣（約2000萬元台幣）舉辦Jayden的百日宴。目前李嘉欣尚未回應遺產一事，昨日在IG上發佈日本街頭自拍照，心情似乎已經恢復許多。（編輯：黃雅琪）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/3n1BFAVoKlRYNJArksBxow--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTEwO2g9MzE5/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/setn_com_683/6e8dd8a45aad56fa2164d0ff30baa9c9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F3n1BFAVoKlRYNJArksBxow--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTEwO2g9MzE5%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Fsetn_com_683%2F6e8dd8a45aad56fa2164d0ff30baa9c9&h=c0749826&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%A4%AB%E5%AE%B6%E5%8D%83%E5%84%84%E9%81%BA%E7%94%A2-%E6%9D%8E%E5%98%89%E6%AC%A3%E6%9C%88%E9%A0%98%E7%99%BE%E8%90%AC%E9%9B%B6%E7%94%A8%E9%8C%A2-004004294.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E5%25A4%25AB%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E5%258D%2583%25E5%2584%2584%25E9%2581%25BA%25E7%2594%25A2-%25E6%259D%258E%25E5%2598%2589%25E6%25AC%25A3%25E6%259C%2588%25E9%25A0%2598%25E7%2599%25BE%25E8%2590%25AC%25E9%259B%25B6%25E7%2594%25A8%25E9%258C%25A2-004004294.html&d=pJzRYsdkl93uV2yzkgrKUdr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=000fd21d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%A4%AB%E5%AE%B6%E5%8D%83%E5%84%84%